<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>A Switch has been rejected on Stratus</h1>
    <p>
      <%= @user_desc %> has rejected a Switch request for <%= @switch.full_name %> on Stratus at <%= @switch.rejected_at.to_s(:pretty) %>.  Visit the Switch request on Stratus to find out why.  
    </p>
    <p>
      To read about this Switch, just follow this link: <%= @url %>.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for using Stratus and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>
